---
title: Onion Chutney Chicken & Parmesan Crumb with Roast Potatoes, Gravy & Buttery Veggies
description: Can we count all the ways to do a crumbed chicken? Let’s give it a shot, first add some sharp Parmesan to make it
cheesy. What about an onion chutney for a hint of smokiness, we say it definitely counts. Finally what if we put them
together, that’s got to be our favourite on the list so far!

 *This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
